  <title>param_spec_fixed</title>
<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(utf8, utf8, utf8, Cogl.Fixed, Cogl.Fixed, Cogl.Fixed, GObject.ParamFlags)
@returns(GObject.ParamSpec)
def param_spec_fixed(name, nick, blurb, minimum, maximum, default_value, flags)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Creates a <link xref="GParamSpec">GParamSpec</link> for properties using <link xref="CoglFixed">CoglFixed</link> values</p>

